Ndinoda kukuudzai kuti Emmanuel TV yakashandura hupenyu hwangu sei.

0:00:21.720,0:00:27.540
Anenge makore maviri apfuura, mudzimai wangu neni takatanga kuona Emmanuel TV

0:00:27.540,0:00:35.300
uye yakabata hupenyu hwe wanano yedu kwazvo, hukama ne hupenyu hwangu hwe kunamata.

0:00:35.300,0:00:40.480
Mazuva ose apo ndinoona Emmanuel TV, ndinogamuchira shoko,

0:00:40.480,0:00:45.120
kumwe kuzarurirwa kwandiri zuva rega rega.

0:00:45.120,0:00:50.380
Tiudze, mukoma: Wakaziva sei nezve Emmanuel TV, kose uko ku Ukraine?

0:00:50.380,0:00:55.860
Ndanga ndichitsvaga pa Youtube uye ndakawana mavhidhiyo anofadza

0:00:55.860,0:00:59.260
pane zve dzikinuro uye uprofita hwe mu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:00:59.260,0:01:06.900
Ndakanyatsofarira nokuti ndakanga ndisati ndamboona dzikinuro yakadai ne zvishamiso kare.

0:01:06.900,0:01:12.120
Ndakafarira izvo mu Porofita T.B. Joshua akanga achiita.

0:01:12.120,0:01:16.160
Inenge mwedzi mitanhatu yapfuura, pane zvakaitika mumhuri yedu.

0:01:16.160,0:01:19.020
Munoona mudzimai wangu pano.

0:01:19.020,0:01:23.660
Rimwe zuva, akanga ari pamba nemwanakoma wedu.

0:01:23.660,0:01:29.900
Akangotama pasi kuti amusimudze ndokubva chimwe chinhu chavhunika mumusana wake.

0:01:29.900,0:01:37.800
Pandakasvika mumba, ndakamuwana avete pasi uye mwana akanga achichema.

0:01:37.800,0:01:45.020
Ndakaedza kumusimudza asi zvakanditorera maminitsi anenge gumi kuti ndimusimudze.

0:01:45.020,0:01:51.080
Marwadzo acho aive akanyanyisa zvokuti ndaifanira kumurarisa ne rutivi rwake

0:01:51.080,0:01:55.620
uye akavata ipapo kwemazuva anenge maviri.

0:01:55.620,0:02:01.160
Ndaifanira kumutendeudza kuti ndimusudurudze nokuti akanga asingakwanisi kuzvifambisa oga.

0:02:01.160,0:02:07.180
Takadana chiremba uye chiremba akauya ndokumu dzvanya dzvanya

0:02:07.180,0:02:10.160
asi hapana chakanaka chakaitika; iye akabva awedzera kurwadziwa.

0:02:10.160,0:02:14.460
Panguva iyoyo, iye aive atoremara zvachose. Akange asingagoni kufamba, aisagona kufamba.

0:02:14.460,0:02:20.000
Chaizvoizvo. Akange asingagoni kusuduruka kana kufamba.

0:02:20.000,0:02:25.460
Manheru ezuva rechipiri, ndakasarudza kuenda pa YouTube

0:02:25.460,0:02:35.260
kuti ndiwane mavhidhiyo eminamato wekuporeswa we vatarisi ne mu Porofita T.B. Joshua.

0:02:35.260,0:02:41.660
Apa, murikuona pikicha inoratidza kuti taibata sei sikirini.

0:02:41.660,0:02:44.300
Sezvamunoziva, chinhambwe handi chipingidzo.

0:02:44.300,0:02:49.640
Mwari akazadza mwoyo wangu nekutenda kuti ndaigona kubata pa sikirini

0:02:49.640,0:02:54.200
zvadaro, ndobata mudzimai wangu ipapo Mwari aizomubata ne kumuporesa.

0:02:54.200,0:02:58.980
Takanyengeterera kweminiti imwe uye pane imwe nguva,

0:02:58.980,0:03:02.880
Ndakanzwa chimwe chinhu chichifamba mukati medu.

0:03:02.880,0:03:11.220
Ndakaona kuti mudzimai wangu akangosimuka ndokutanga kukotama kuruboshwe ne kurudyi.

0:03:11.220,0:03:15.380
Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

0:03:15.380,0:03:19.520
Changamire, apo makanyengetera ne muporofita T.B. Joshua paYouTube,

0:03:19.520,0:03:21.880
munamato waakanyengeterera vatariri pasi pose,

0:03:21.880,0:03:27.440
simba ra Mwari rakaburuka mumba menyu ku Ukraine, uye mudzimai wako akamugamuchira kuporeswa.

0:03:27.440,0:03:33.460
Hungu, akagamuchira kurapwa kwake ndokutanga kufamba neku kuzviongorora.

0:03:33.460,0:03:36.580
Ndakatomubvunza kuti chii chaaiita nokuti aisagona kufamba kare.

0:03:36.580,0:03:40.940
Akaenda akazvipfekedza oga, pasina rubatsiro rwangu

0:03:40.940,0:03:47.040
uye takaenda kunopupurira kuvabereki vedu pamusoro pezvakaitwa na Mwari muupenyu hwedu.

0:03:47.040,0:03:51.260
Wawu! Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwe chete kuna Jesu Kristu kamwe zvakare!

0:03:51.260,0:03:55.220
Kubvira ipapo, changamire, mudzimai wenyu ari sei kubva pamunyengetero wacho

0:03:55.220,0:03:57.700
uyo akapa nemu Porofita T.B. Joshua? Mamiriro ake kubva ipapo ari sei?

0:03:57.700,0:04:02.860
Anonzwa zvakanaka kwazvo. Ari ku Ukraine nevanakomana vedu vaviri.

0:04:02.860,0:04:06.440
Mwari arikuti komborera zvikuru. Rumbidzai Ishe.

0:04:06.440,0:04:09.220
Hareruya. Tirikuona mifananidzo yacho apa.

0:04:09.220,0:04:11.720
Mungagone here kungotiratidza zvakare. Ndiani mukadzi uyu?

0:04:11.720,0:04:13.600
Zita rake ndi Julia.

0:04:13.600,0:04:18.260
Wawu, tiri kumuona achipupurira apa mushure memunamato wemu Porofita T.B. Joshua pa Emmanuel TV,

0:04:18.260,0:04:21.680
kuti akagamuchira sei kuporeswa pakarepo muzita ra Jesu Kristu.

0:04:21.680,0:04:25.180
Mukoma, chii chamungaudza pasi rose pamusoro pe Emmanuel TV

0:04:25.180,0:04:31.140
uye kunyanya kuti unokurudzira sei vanhu kunyengetera pamwechete nemu Porofita T.B. Joshua

0:04:31.140,0:04:33.900
pa Emanuel TV, chero kupi zvako kwavari pasi rese.

