0:04:52.280,0:04:58.780
Iwe unogona kuona Emmanuel TV uye Mwari achasimudza hupenyu hwako hwe kunamata.

0:04:58.780,0:05:06.020
Kana pane dambudziko kana hurwere muhupenyu hwako kana chero chinetso chipi zvacho,

0:05:06.020,0:05:09.680
iwe unogona kunyengetera pamwechete nomu Porofita T.B. Joshua zvadaro Mwari vachafamba muupenyu hwako.

0:05:09.680,0:05:14.300
Ameni. Ngatiisei maoko edu pamwechete kuna Jesu Kristu!

