paIndaneti Emmanuel TV inotamba 24/7

0:05:39.540,0:05:43.820
uye kune mavhidhiyo anoshamisa papeji yedu ye nhepfenyuro ye YouTube

0:05:43.820,0:05:47.440
yaunogona kubatana nayo nokutenda uye Mwari achakubatawo.

0:05:47.440,0:05:52.000
Mukoma, isu tinovonga Mwari nekuda kwehupenyu hwenyu, uye tinoziva kuti zvakanakisisa zvichiri kuuya, muzita ra Jesu.

0:05:52.000,0:05:53.000
Mazvita

0:05:53.000,0:05:59.020
Tinovimba kuti wakurudzirwa nevhidhiyo yawabva mukuona.

